title: Stranger Danger: Can You Trust Any Week 8 Breakout Players? Plus: The Extreme Fantasy Football League | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Week 8 featured an array of low-owned players putting up huge numbers, but which of them can we trust? Plus, injury updates, streamers of the week, and another edition of Fantasy Court.
Host: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
